<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Larcher, Pierre-Henri (1829). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/?id=Tpp5B39UlTMC&pg=PA526&lpg=PA526&dq=Herodotus+Muses"><i>Larcher's Notes on Herodotus</i></a>. London: John R. Priestley. p.&#160;526<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://books.google.com/?id=Tpp5B39UlTMC&pg=PA526&lpg=PA526&dq=Herodotus+Muses">http://books.google.com/?id=Tpp5B39UlTMC&amp;pg=PA526&amp;lpg=PA526&amp;dq=Herodotus+Muses</a></span>.</span></span></li>
